<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Alumni Connect - Login</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }
        body {
            display: flex;
            height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #2196F3);
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            width: 900px;
        }
        .left-panel {
            background: #2196F3;
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .profile-image img {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 3px solid white;
        }
        .testimonial {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .right-section {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .login-box input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .login-box button {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px;
            width: 100%;
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .login-box button:hover {
            background: #388E3C;
        }
        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .social-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: white;
            color: #444;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .social-icon:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            background: #ddd;
        }
        .success-checkmark {
            display: none;
            font-size: 50px;
            color: #4CAF50;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="left-panel">
            <div class="logo">AlumniConnect</div>
            <div class="profile-section">
                <div class="profile-image">
                    <img src="https://img.freepik.com/premium-vector/student-logo-icon-brand-identity-sign-symbol-template_880781-553.jpg" alt="Alumni Profile">
                </div>
                <h1>Welcome Back, Alumni!</h1>
            </div>
            <p>Reconnect with your alma mater, mentor students, and expand your network.</p>
            <div class="testimonial">
                <p>"The alumni network has been instrumental in my career growth!"</p>
                <div>- Sarah Johnson, Class of 2018</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="right-section">
            <div class="login-box">
                <h2>Hey Admin</h2>
                <p>Please enter your credentials to continue</p>
                <form action="/admin" method="POST">
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" required>
                    <input type="password" name="password" placeholder="Password" required>
                    <button type="submit">Login</button>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="social-login">
                <p>Or login with</p>
                <div class="social-icons">
                    <div class="social-icon">G</div>
                    <div class="social-icon">in</div>
                    <div class="social-icon">f</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>